Network wide updates for systems using APT.

nwu is free software and licensed under the GPLv3 or later.
Some small components are also licensed under the LGPLv3 or later.

The complete text of the licenses can be found in COPYING and COPYING.LIB.


Every component now has its own README file which can be found in
nwu/<component>/README, such as nwu/server/README.
Changelog files are also per-component now.

Documentation can be found in doc/<component>/.
